<event name="FR_LEAH_JERRY_ROYAL">
	<text>Leah seems surprised at the sight of Jerry "Jerry?! What are you doing here?! There's no way Vance would ever let you be somewhere so dangerous!"

		Jerry sighs "It's...A long story. Look Leah, this whole thing my uncle is doing is a giant mistake and won't end well no matter what. I know how persistant you are, determination like that shouldn't be thrown away in persuit of such a terrible plan. So...What if you joined us in the quest to stop my uncle?"
	</text>
		<choice hidden="true" blue="false">
			<text>Continue...</text> 
			<event>
				<text>Leah blinks, baffled by what Jerry just said "You are really asking me to join you and my arch nemesis?! Jerry, look, I like you but this is a very tough ask. How could I even know this isn't a trap?"

					"Come on Leah, why would your best friend lie to you?" You manage to catch a glimpse of jerry covertly winking to you, meanwhile leah takes a step back "You...you think i'm your best friend?...In that case, you better give me the best room in your ship, beyatch!" Jerry sighs as leah beams into your ship.
				</text>
				<crewMember amount="1" class="unique_leah_mfk">Leah</crewMember>
				<choice hidden="true" blue="false">
					<text>Wait, sylvan!</text>
					<event load="FR_SYLVAN_INJURED"/>
				</choice>
			</event>
		</choice>
</event>

